### 1. 查询所有学生（初始为空）
GET http://localhost:8080/students

### 2. 添加学生1
POST http://localhost:8080/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "001",
  "name": "张三",
  "age": 20,
  "sex": "男"
}

### 3. 添加学生2
POST http://localhost:8080/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "002",
  "name": "李四",
  "age": 22,
  "sex": "女"
}

### 4. 查询所有学生（应返回2条）
GET http://localhost:8080/students

### 5. 根据ID查询学生
GET http://localhost:8080/students/001

### 6. 修改学生信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/students/001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三丰",
  "age": 21,
  "sex": "男"
}

### 7. 再次查询001（验证是否修改成功）
GET http://localhost:8080/students/001

### 8. 删除学生
DELETE http://localhost:8080/students/001

### 9. 查询所有学生（应只剩1条）
GET http://localhost:8080/students